I would like to introduce you to one of my   favourite artists.

The art museum of the future presents great and talented artists from the here and now.

Artist: Crisstiana | SR
Crisstiana is a 28 year old artist from Romania who currently lives in Italy. Since childhood, Crisstiana was interested in visual arts. Fate took her to study Psychology, which is one of her biggest passions. Crisstiana´s AI Collaborative works are inspired by everyday life: through the combination of textures, shapes and vibrant colors that she likes to use, Crisstiana translates her emotions and experiences to the world.
